locality: T6. Mindu Forest Reserve, ca. 200 m N of main road to Mikumi N of Mindu Lake. Rocky thicket woodland dominated by Dichrostachys cinerea, Diplorhynchus condylocarpon, Pseudolachnostylis maprouneifolia, Acacia nigrescens, Dalbergia melanoxylon, Afzelia quanzensis, Julbernardia globiflora, Tamarindus indica, Steganotaenia araliacea, Pteleopsis sp., Brachystegia boehmii, Balanites aegyptiaca, Kigelia africana, Xerophyta spekei, Ximenia americana and Ficus sp.
Paysannat Luzumu-Kinzolani. Territoire: Kasangulu. Entre village Kela-Kinzolani. Luzumu
Munini (Mashuha; préf. de Bururi); source de la Sikuvyaye
